metadata.name: The NFT Pioneers #1
metadata.description: This is "The NFT Pioneers Podcast Token", which will be limited to 100 tokens and serves as a gift to every guest for sharing their knowledge on our podcast. Each holder of the token will have access to a one-hour NFT consulting session, limited access to the LinkedIn Group for networking with industry experts + daily NFT news, and yearly access to the experts-only NFT event in Vienna, which will take place on 22 August every year. The Unique Identifier is randomly generated and represents seat number at the event. Â©nouz.co #1
